G}',4,'4','4',NULL),(489,'f7493bcf-5c17-4562-a759-37082ec49ff8','Bumi, King of Three Trials','Bumi, Rey de las Tres Pruebas','Legendary Creature — Human Noble Ally','When Bumi enters, choose up to X, where X is the number of Lesson cards in your graveyard —\n• Put three +1/+1 counters on Bumi.\n• Target player scries 3.\n• Earthbend 3. (Target land you control becomes a 0/0 creature with haste that\'s still a land. Put three +1/+1 counters on it. When it dies or is exiled, return it to the battlefield tapped.)','{5}{G}',6,'4','4',NULL),(490,'77eda626-5cef-496d-b291-cfa1ee6fc1fb','Cycle of Renewal','Ciclo de renovación','Instant — Lesson','Sacrifice a land. Search your library for up to two basic land cards, put them onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.','{2}{G}',3,NULL,NULL,NULL),(491,'6a84a8a4-c8b0-45ce-af6f-605fcffc395b','Diligent Zookeeper','Guardián diligente','Creature — Human Citizen Ally','Each non-Human creature you control gets +1/+1 for each of its creature types, to a maximum of 10.','{3}{G}',4,'4','4',NULL),(492,'d5770b0f-4493-42e9-a2d7-0e74a28da4ba','The Earth King','El Rey de la Tierra','Legendary Creature — Human Noble Ally','When The Earth King enters, create a 4/4 green Bear creature token.\nWhenever one or more creatures you control with power 4 or greater attack, search your library for up to that many basic land cards, put them onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.','{3}{G}',4,'2','2',NULL),(493,'e43c31ee-1bac-4f96-8b74-334b3238ab73','Earth Kingdom General','General del Reino de la Tierra','Creature — Human Soldier Ally','When this creature enters, earthbend 2. (Target land you control becomes a 0/0 creature with haste that\'s still a land. Put two +1/+1 counters on it. When it dies or is exiled, return it to the battlefield tapped.)\nWhenever you put one or more +1/+1 counters on a creature, you may gain that much life. Do this only once each turn.','{3}{G}',4,'2','2',NULL),(494,'f04a7763-5fba-42e5-a45a-b3dc2daba902','Earth Rumble','R