y Farmer','Granjera precavida','Creature — Kithkin Citizen','At the beginning of your end step, if another creature entered the battlefield under your control this turn, surveil 1. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put it into your graveyard.)','{1}{G/W}{G/W}',3,'3','3',NULL),(966,'e5e8fce4-c97a-4ae4-9583-003c565e3bd6','Wistfulness','Pesadumbre','Creature — Elemental Incarnation','When this creature enters, if {G}{G} was spent to cast it, exile target artifact or enchantment an opponent controls.\nWhen this creature enters, if {U}{U} was spent to cast it, draw two cards, then discard a card.\nEvoke {G/U}{G/U} (You may cast this spell for its evoke cost. If you do, it\'s sacrificed when it enters.)','{3}{G/U}{G/U}',5,'6','5',NULL),(967,'e949b362-4988-4482-ac51-c1049af9040c','Chronicle of Victory','Crónica de la victoria','Legendary Artifact','As Chronicle of Victory enters, choose a creature type.\nCreatures you control of the chosen type get +2/+2 and have first strike and trample.\nWhenever you cast a spell of the chosen type, draw a card.','{6}',6,NULL,NULL,NULL),(968,'311eef28-21e9-44fa-96df-d281f0a9ba34','Dawn-Blessed Pennant','Bandera bendita por el alba','Artifact','As this artifact enters, choose Elemental, Elf, Faerie, Giant, Goblin, Kithkin, Merfolk, or Treefolk.\nWhenever a permanent you control of the chosen type enters, you gain 1 life.\n{2}, {T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Return target card of the chosen type from your graveyard to your hand.','{1}',1,NULL,NULL,NULL),(969,'126c75c0-414b-4e55-8747-2b5566ce716f','Firdoch Core','Núcleo de firdoch','Kindred Artifact — Shapeshifter','Changeling (This card is every creature type.)\n{T}: Add one mana of any color.\n{4}: This artifact becomes a 4/4 artifact creature until end of turn.','{3}',3,NULL,NULL,NULL),(970,'11ceb2db-021e-422d-976e-7bfe3b67a8aa','Foraging Wickermaw','Picomimbre buscador','Artifact Creature — Scarecrow','When this creature enters, surveil 1. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put it into your graveyard.)\n{1}: Add one mana of any color. This creature becomes that color until end of turn. Activate only once each turn.','{2}',2,'1','3',NULL),(971,'9f6d6e90-7462-46e5-bf2f-725b4badc394','Gathering Stone','Piedra de encuentro','Artifact','As this artifact enters, choose a creature type.\nSpells you cast of the chosen type cost {1} less to cast.\nWhen this artifact enters and at the beginning of your upkeep, look at the top card of your library. If it\'s a card of the chosen type, you may reveal it and put it into your hand. If you don\'t put the card into your hand, you may put it into your graveyard.','{4}',4,NULL,NULL,NULL),(972,'353db389-b829-4e66-85d5-6018bc87c3e0','Mirrormind Crown','Corona mentespejo','Artifact — Equipment','As long as this Equipment is attached to a creature, the first time you would create one or more tokens each turn, you may instead create that many tokens that are copies of equipped creature.\nEquip {2}','{4}',4,NULL,NULL,NULL),(973,'499b4cf9-2aaa-45a0-8362-77b727b7f7cc','Puca\'s Eye','Ojo de puca','Artifact','When this artifact enters, draw a card, then choose a color. This artifact becomes the chosen color.\n{3}, {T}: Draw a card. Activate only if there are five colors among permanents you control.','{2}',2,NULL,NULL,NULL),(974,'bdeb440d-a714-40e8-9038-f651e6ae45fb','Springleaf Drum','Tambor de hoja primaveral','Artifact','{T}, Tap an untapped creature you control: Add one mana of any color.','{1}',1,NULL,NULL,NULL),(975,'064c3269-c012-4fc7-84c3-5f147a82a03c','Stalactite Dagger','Daga de estalactita','Artifact — Equipment','When this Equipment enters, create a 1/1 colorless Shapeshifter creature token with changeling. (It\'s every creature type.)\nEquipped creature gets +1/+1 and is all creature types.\nEquip {2} ({2}: Attach to target creature you control. Equip only as a sorcery.)','{2}',2,NULL,NULL,NULL),(976,'43985bbc-a0f6-4812-984e-392bc8562633','Blood Crypt','Cripta sangrienta','Land — Swamp Mountain','({T}: Add {B} or {R}.)\nAs this land enters, you may pay 2 life. If you don\'t, it enters tapped.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(977,'5715ed43-395c-4877-99a7-8e28e7bf9dce','Eclipsed Realms','Reinos eclipsados','Land','As this land enters, choose Elemental, Elf, Faerie, Giant, Goblin, Kithkin, Merfolk, or Treefolk.\n{T}: Add {C}.\n{T}: Add one mana of any color. Spend this mana only to cast a spell of the chosen type or activate an ability of a source of the chosen type.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(978,'a75445d3-1303-4bb5-89ad-26ea93fecd48','Evolving Wilds',NULL,'Land','{T}, Sacrifice this land: Search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(979,'f1750962-a87c-49f6-b731-02ae971ac6ea','Hallowed Fountain',NULL,'Land — Plains Island','({T}: Add {W} or {U}.)\nAs this land enters, you may pay 2 life. If you don\'t, it enters tapped.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(980,'975ec9a3-6f20-4177-8211-82526e092538','Overgrown Tomb',NULL,'Land — Swamp Forest','({T}: Add {B} or {G}.)\nAs this land enters, you may pay 2 life. If you don\'t, it enters tapped.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(981,'17039058-822d-409f-938c-b727a366ba63','Steam Vents',NULL,'Land — Island Mountain','({T}: Add {U} or {R}.)\nAs this land enters, you may pay 2 life. If you don\'t, it enters tapped.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(982,'f413a83d-a40d-434c-b20a-4c707c0527fa','Temple Garden',NULL,'Land — Forest Plains','({T}: Add {G} or {W}.)\nAs this land enters, you may pay 2 life. If you don\'t, it enters tapped.','',0,NULL,NULL,NULL);
